snippet.title: Pinball Heroes: Complete Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Pinball Heroes™: Complete is now available for the PlayStation®Vita system! The classic PSP® game has been remade with the PS Vita's system's features in mind and includes all 8 action-packed tables from the original version, as well as a slew of new online and social features so you can show the world your pinball prowess by competing with friends.

©2009, 2013 Sony Computer Entertainment America LLC. Pinball Heroes, High Velocity Bowling, Hot Shots Golf, ModNation Racers, Pain, and UNCHARTED: Drake's Fortune are trademarks of Sony Computer Entertainment America LLC. WiPeout is a trademark of Sony Computer Entertainment Europe.
